high_descs: Turn and go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the tray next to the coffee maker.
Turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door.  Place the tray on the bottom shelf.  Close the fridge door. Open the fridge door and grab the tray on the bottom shelf.
Turn to your left and go to the toaster.
Place the tray on the counter to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move the tray to the counter by toaster.

high_descs: Turn right, move past the refrigerator, then turn left and move to the coffee maker, then turn left and face the pan to the left of the coffee maker.
Pick up the pan from the counter.
Move along the edge of the counter then turn left and move to the refrigerator next to the blue rubbish bin.

Open the refrigerator and place the pan on the lowest shelf, underneath the head of lettuce. Close the refrigerator, wait for the pan to chill, then open the refrigerator and pick up the pan from the bottom shelf. Close the refrigerator door.
Turn left, move towards the sink, then turn right and face the kitchen counter area between the oven and the refrigerator.
Place the pan between the oven and the toaster next to the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pan on the kitchen counter.

high_descs: Pick up the square pan on the counter.
Bring the square pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Bring the pan to the counter right of the stove.
Put the pan on the counter right of the stove next to the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the counter next to the toaster.
